<subSubSection pageId="33" pageNumber="34" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Discussion.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Cerro Gordo is quite remote from other high peaks in the area as it takes nearly 10 hours of driving from Durango along a dirt road to reach the base of the mountain, just south of Maiz Gordo. There are other mountains in Durango that approach this height and it would seem reasonable to assume that this species might occur on these.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
